<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>لأعَظَمْتَ النَّدَامَةَ فِيهِ لَهْفًا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَلَى مَا فِي حَيَاتِكَ قَدْ أَضَعْتَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تَفِرُّ مِنْ الْهَجِيرِ وَتَتَقِيهِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَهَلا مِن جَهَنَّمَ قَدْ فَرَرْتَا!!<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَلَسْتَ تُطيقُ أَهْوَانَها عَذَابًا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>ولو كُنْتَ الْحَدِيدَ بِها لَذُبْتَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَلا تكْذِبْ فَإنَّ الأَمْرَ جَدٌّ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَلَيَسَ كَمَا حَسِبْتَ وَمَا ظَنَنْتَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَبَا بَكْرٍ كَشَفْت أَقَلَّ عَيْبِي<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَمَا اسْتَعْظَمْتَهُ مِنْهَا سَتَرْتَا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَقُلْ مَا شِئْتَ فِي مِن الْمَخَازِي<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَضَاعِفْهَا فَإنَّكَ قَدْ صَدَقْتَا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَمَهْمَا عَبْتَنِي فَلِفَرْطِ عِلْمِي<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>بِبَاطِنَتِي كَأنَّكَ قَدْ مَدَحْتَا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَلا تَرْضَى الْمَعَائبَ فَهِيَ عارٌ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>عَظِيمٌ يُورِثُ الإِنْسَانَ مَقْتَا<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَتَهْوَى بَالوَجِيهِ مِنَ الثُّرَيَا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَتُبْدِلُهُ مَكانَ الْفَوْقِ تَحْتَا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>كَذَا الطَّاعَاتُ ُتبِلِغُكَ الدَّرَارِي<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَتَجْعَلُكَ القَرِيبَ وإنْ بَعُدْتَا<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَتَنْشُرُ عَنْكَ فِي الدُّنْيَا جَمِيلاً<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>فَتَلْقَى البِرَّ فِيها حَيْثُ شِئْتَا<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>وتُمسِي في مَسَاكِنِهَا عَزِيزًا<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>